51template <int Dims, int Order>
52struct MonomialBasis : detail::MonomialBasis<Dims, Order>
53{
54 public:
55 using BaseType = detail::MonomialBasis<Dims, Order>;
56 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = BaseType::kDims;
57 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = BaseType::kOrder;
58 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = BaseType::kSize;
65 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
66 {
67 return BaseType::eval(X);
68 }
69
75 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
76 {
77 return BaseType::derivatives(X);
78 }
79
85 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
86 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
87 {
88 return BaseType::antiderivatives(X);
89 }
90};

217template <>
218class MonomialBasis<1, 1>
219{
220 public:
221 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 1;
222 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 1;
223 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 2;
224
225 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
226 {
227 Vector<kSize> P;
228 P[0] = 1;
229 P[1] = X[0];
230 return P;
231 }
232
233 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
234 {
235 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
236 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
237 G[0] = 0;
238 G[1] = 1;
239 return Gm;
240 }
241
242 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
243 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
244 {
245 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
246 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
247 P[0] = X[0];
248 P[1] = (1.0 / 2.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
249 return Pm;
250 }
251};

253template <>
254class MonomialBasis<1, 2>
255{
256 public:
257 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 1;
258 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 2;
259 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 3;
260
261 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
262 {
263 Vector<kSize> P;
264 P[0] = 1;
265 P[1] = X[0];
266 P[2] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
267 return P;
268 }
269
270 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
271 {
272 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
273 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
274 G[0] = 0;
275 G[1] = 1;
276 G[2] = 2 * X[0];
277 return Gm;
278 }
279
280 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
281 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
282 {
283 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
284 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
285 P[0] = X[0];
286 P[1] = (1.0 / 2.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
287 P[2] = (1.0 / 3.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
288 return Pm;
289 }
290};

292template <>
293class MonomialBasis<1, 3>
294{
295 public:
296 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 1;
297 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 3;
298 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 4;
299
300 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
301 {
302 Vector<kSize> P;
303 P[0] = 1;
304 P[1] = X[0];
305 P[2] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
306 P[3] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
307 return P;
308 }
309
310 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
311 {
312 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
313 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
314 G[0] = 0;
315 G[1] = 1;
316 G[2] = 2 * X[0];
317 G[3] = 3 * ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
318 return Gm;
319 }
320
321 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
322 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
323 {
324 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
325 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
326 P[0] = X[0];
327 P[1] = (1.0 / 2.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
328 P[2] = (1.0 / 3.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
329 P[3] = (1.0 / 4.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
330 return Pm;
331 }
332};

334template <>
335class MonomialBasis<1, 4>
336{
337 public:
338 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 1;
339 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 4;
340 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 5;
341
342 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
343 {
344 Vector<kSize> P;
345 P[0] = 1;
346 P[1] = X[0];
347 P[2] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
348 P[3] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
349 P[4] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
350 return P;
351 }
352
353 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
354 {
355 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
356 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
357 G[0] = 0;
358 G[1] = 1;
359 G[2] = 2 * X[0];
360 G[3] = 3 * ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
361 G[4] = 4 * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
362 return Gm;
363 }
364
365 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
366 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
367 {
368 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
369 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
370 P[0] = X[0];
371 P[1] = (1.0 / 2.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
372 P[2] = (1.0 / 3.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
373 P[3] = (1.0 / 4.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
374 P[4] = (1.0 / 5.0) * std::pow(X[0], 5);
375 return Pm;
376 }
377};

383template <>
384class MonomialBasis<2, 1>
385{
386 public:
387 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 2;
388 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 1;
389 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 3;
390
391 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
392 {
393 Vector<kSize> P;
394 P[0] = 1;
395 P[1] = X[0];
396 P[2] = X[1];
397 return P;
398 }
399
400 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
401 {
402 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
403 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
404 G[0] = 0;
405 G[1] = 0;
406 G[2] = 1;
407 G[3] = 0;
408 G[4] = 0;
409 G[5] = 1;
410 return Gm;
411 }
412
413 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
414 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
415 {
416 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
417 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
418 Scalar const a0 = X[0] * X[1];
419 P[0] = X[0];
420 P[1] = (1.0 / 2.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
421 P[2] = a0;
422 P[3] = X[1];
423 P[4] = a0;
424 P[5] = (1.0 / 2.0) * ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
425 return Pm;
426 }
427};

429template <>
430class MonomialBasis<2, 2>
431{
432 public:
433 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 2;
434 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 2;
435 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 6;
436
437 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
438 {
439 Vector<kSize> P;
440 P[0] = 1;
441 P[1] = X[0];
442 P[2] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
443 P[3] = X[1];
444 P[4] = X[0] * X[1];
445 P[5] = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
446 return P;
447 }
448
449 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
450 {
451 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
452 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
453 G[0] = 0;
454 G[1] = 0;
455 G[2] = 1;
456 G[3] = 0;
457 G[4] = 2 * X[0];
458 G[5] = 0;
459 G[6] = 0;
460 G[7] = 1;
461 G[8] = X[1];
462 G[9] = X[0];
463 G[10] = 0;
464 G[11] = 2 * X[1];
465 return Gm;
466 }
467
468 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
469 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
470 {
471 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
472 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
473 Scalar const a0 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
474 Scalar const a1 = (1.0 / 2.0) * a0;
475 Scalar const a2 = X[0] * X[1];
476 Scalar const a3 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
477 Scalar const a4 = a3 * X[0];
478 P[0] = X[0];
479 P[1] = a1;
480 P[2] = (1.0 / 3.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
481 P[3] = a2;
482 P[4] = a1 * X[1];
483 P[5] = a4;
484 P[6] = X[1];
485 P[7] = a2;
486 P[8] = a0 * X[1];
487 P[9] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a3;
488 P[10] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a4;
489 P[11] = (1.0 / 3.0) * ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
490 return Pm;
491 }
492};

494template <>
495class MonomialBasis<2, 3>
496{
497 public:
498 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 2;
499 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 3;
500 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 10;
501
502 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
503 {
504 Vector<kSize> P;
505 Scalar const a0 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
506 Scalar const a1 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
507 P[0] = 1;
508 P[1] = X[0];
509 P[2] = a0;
510 P[3] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
511 P[4] = X[1];
512 P[5] = X[0] * X[1];
513 P[6] = a0 * X[1];
514 P[7] = a1;
515 P[8] = a1 * X[0];
516 P[9] = ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
517 return P;
518 }
519
520 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
521 {
522 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
523 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
524 Scalar const a0 = 2 * X[0];
525 Scalar const a1 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
526 Scalar const a2 = a0 * X[1];
527 Scalar const a3 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
528 G[0] = 0;
529 G[1] = 0;
530 G[2] = 1;
531 G[3] = 0;
532 G[4] = a0;
533 G[5] = 0;
534 G[6] = 3 * a1;
535 G[7] = 0;
536 G[8] = 0;
537 G[9] = 1;
538 G[10] = X[1];
539 G[11] = X[0];
540 G[12] = a2;
541 G[13] = a1;
542 G[14] = 0;
543 G[15] = 2 * X[1];
544 G[16] = a3;
545 G[17] = a2;
546 G[18] = 0;
547 G[19] = 3 * a3;
548 return Gm;
549 }
550
551 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
552 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
553 {
554 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
555 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
556 Scalar const a0 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
557 Scalar const a1 = (1.0 / 2.0) * a0;
558 Scalar const a2 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
559 Scalar const a3 = (1.0 / 3.0) * a2;
560 Scalar const a4 = X[0] * X[1];
561 Scalar const a5 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
562 Scalar const a6 = a5 * X[0];
563 Scalar const a7 = a1 * a5;
564 Scalar const a8 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
565 Scalar const a9 = a8 * X[0];
566 P[0] = X[0];
567 P[1] = a1;
568 P[2] = a3;
569 P[3] = (1.0 / 4.0) * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
570 P[4] = a4;
571 P[5] = a1 * X[1];
572 P[6] = a3 * X[1];
573 P[7] = a6;
574 P[8] = a7;
575 P[9] = a9;
576 P[10] = X[1];
577 P[11] = a4;
578 P[12] = a0 * X[1];
579 P[13] = a2 * X[1];
580 P[14] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a5;
581 P[15] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a6;
582 P[16] = a7;
583 P[17] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a8;
584 P[18] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a9;
585 P[19] = (1.0 / 4.0) * ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
586 return Pm;
587 }
588};

590template <>
591class MonomialBasis<2, 4>
592{
593 public:
594 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 2;
595 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 4;
596 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 15;
597
598 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
599 {
600 Vector<kSize> P;
601 Scalar const a0 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
602 Scalar const a1 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
603 Scalar const a2 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
604 Scalar const a3 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
605 P[0] = 1;
606 P[1] = X[0];
607 P[2] = a0;
608 P[3] = a1;
609 P[4] = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
610 P[5] = X[1];
611 P[6] = X[0] * X[1];
612 P[7] = a0 * X[1];
613 P[8] = a1 * X[1];
614 P[9] = a2;
615 P[10] = a2 * X[0];
616 P[11] = a0 * a2;
617 P[12] = a3;
618 P[13] = a3 * X[0];
619 P[14] = ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
620 return P;
621 }
622
623 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
624 {
625 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
626 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
627 Scalar const a0 = 2 * X[0];
628 Scalar const a1 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
629 Scalar const a2 = 3 * a1;
630 Scalar const a3 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
631 Scalar const a4 = a0 * X[1];
632 Scalar const a5 = 2 * X[1];
633 Scalar const a6 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
634 Scalar const a7 = 3 * a6;
635 Scalar const a8 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
636 G[0] = 0;
637 G[1] = 0;
638 G[2] = 1;
639 G[3] = 0;
640 G[4] = a0;
641 G[5] = 0;
642 G[6] = a2;
643 G[7] = 0;
644 G[8] = 4 * a3;
645 G[9] = 0;
646 G[10] = 0;
647 G[11] = 1;
648 G[12] = X[1];
649 G[13] = X[0];
650 G[14] = a4;
651 G[15] = a1;
652 G[16] = a2 * X[1];
653 G[17] = a3;
654 G[18] = 0;
655 G[19] = a5;
656 G[20] = a6;
657 G[21] = a4;
658 G[22] = a0 * a6;
659 G[23] = a1 * a5;
660 G[24] = 0;
661 G[25] = a7;
662 G[26] = a8;
663 G[27] = a7 * X[0];
664 G[28] = 0;
665 G[29] = 4 * a8;
666 return Gm;
667 }
668
669 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
670 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
671 {
672 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
673 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
674 Scalar const a0 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
675 Scalar const a1 = (1.0 / 2.0) * a0;
676 Scalar const a2 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
677 Scalar const a3 = (1.0 / 3.0) * a2;
678 Scalar const a4 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
679 Scalar const a5 = (1.0 / 4.0) * a4;
680 Scalar const a6 = X[0] * X[1];
681 Scalar const a7 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
682 Scalar const a8 = a7 * X[0];
683 Scalar const a9 = a1 * a7;
684 Scalar const a10 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
685 Scalar const a11 = a10 * X[0];
686 Scalar const a12 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
687 Scalar const a13 = a12 * X[0];
688 Scalar const a14 = (1.0 / 2.0) * a7;
689 Scalar const a15 = (1.0 / 3.0) * a10;
690 P[0] = X[0];
691 P[1] = a1;
692 P[2] = a3;
693 P[3] = a5;
694 P[4] = (1.0 / 5.0) * std::pow(X[0], 5);
695 P[5] = a6;
696 P[6] = a1 * X[1];
697 P[7] = a3 * X[1];
698 P[8] = a5 * X[1];
699 P[9] = a8;
700 P[10] = a9;
701 P[11] = a3 * a7;
702 P[12] = a11;
703 P[13] = a1 * a10;
704 P[14] = a13;
705 P[15] = X[1];
706 P[16] = a6;
707 P[17] = a0 * X[1];
708 P[18] = a2 * X[1];
709 P[19] = a4 * X[1];
710 P[20] = a14;
711 P[21] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a8;
712 P[22] = a9;
713 P[23] = a14 * a2;
714 P[24] = a15;
715 P[25] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a11;
716 P[26] = a0 * a15;
717 P[27] = (1.0 / 4.0) * a12;
718 P[28] = (1.0 / 4.0) * a13;
719 P[29] = (1.0 / 5.0) * std::pow(X[1], 5);
720 return Pm;
721 }
722};

728template <>
729class MonomialBasis<3, 1>
730{
731 public:
732 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 3;
733 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 1;
734 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 4;
735
736 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
737 {
738 Vector<kSize> P;
739 P[0] = 1;
740 P[1] = X[0];
741 P[2] = X[1];
742 P[3] = X[2];
743 return P;
744 }
745
746 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
747 {
748 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
749 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
750 G[0] = 0;
751 G[1] = 0;
752 G[2] = 0;
753 G[3] = 1;
754 G[4] = 0;
755 G[5] = 0;
756 G[6] = 0;
757 G[7] = 1;

1329 Scalar const a24 = a21 * a6;
1330 Scalar const a25 = a21 * X[1];
1331 Scalar const a26 = a1 * a25;
1332 Scalar const a27 = ((X[2]) * (X[2]) * (X[2]));
1333 Scalar const a28 = a27 * X[0];
1334 Scalar const a29 = a27 * a6;
1335 Scalar const a30 = ((X[2]) * (X[2]) * (X[2]) * (X[2]));
1336 Scalar const a31 = a30 * X[0];
1337 Scalar const a32 = a0 * X[1];
1338 Scalar const a33 = a2 * X[1];
1339 Scalar const a34 = (1.0 / 2.0) * a7;
1340 Scalar const a35 = (1.0 / 3.0) * a10;
1341 Scalar const a36 = (1.0 / 4.0) * a12;

1343 Scalar const a38 = a33 * X[2];
1344 Scalar const a39 = a21 * a34;
1345 Scalar const a40 = (1.0 / 2.0) * a21;
1346 Scalar const a41 = a40 * a8;
1347 Scalar const a42 = a27 * X[1];
1348 Scalar const a43 = a30 * X[1];
1349 Scalar const a44 = a0 * X[2];
1350 Scalar const a45 = (1.0 / 3.0) * a27;
1351 P[0] = X[0];
1352 P[1] = a1;
1353 P[2] = a3;
1354 P[3] = a5;
1355 P[4] = (1.0 / 5.0) * std::pow(X[0], 5);
1356 P[5] = a6;
1357 P[6] = a1 * X[1];
1358 P[7] = a3 * X[1];
1359 P[8] = a5 * X[1];

1371 P[20] = a1 * a16;

1379 P[28] = a24;
1380 P[29] = a26;
1381 P[30] = a21 * a8;
1382 P[31] = a28;
1383 P[32] = a1 * a27;
1384 P[33] = a29;
1385 P[34] = a31;
1386 P[35] = X[1];
1387 P[36] = a6;
1388 P[37] = a32;
1389 P[38] = a33;
1390 P[39] = a4 * X[1];
1391 P[40] = a34;
1392 P[41] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a8;
1393 P[42] = a9;
1394 P[43] = a2 * a34;
1395 P[44] = a35;
1396 P[45] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a11;
1397 P[46] = a0 * a35;
1398 P[47] = a36;
1399 P[48] = (1.0 / 4.0) * a13;
1400 P[49] = (1.0 / 5.0) * std::pow(X[1], 5);
1401 P[50] = a16;
1402 P[51] = a15;
1403 P[52] = a37;
1404 P[53] = a38;
1405 P[54] = a34 * X[2];
1406 P[55] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a17;
1407 P[56] = a19;
1408 P[57] = a35 * X[2];
1409 P[58] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a20;
1410 P[59] = a36 * X[2];
1411 P[60] = a25;
1412 P[61] = a24;
1413 P[62] = a21 * a32;
1414 P[63] = a39;
1415 P[64] = a41;
1416 P[65] = a21 * a35;
1417 P[66] = a42;
1418 P[67] = a29;
1419 P[68] = a27 * a34;
1420 P[69] = a43;
1421 P[70] = X[2];
1422 P[71] = a14;
1423 P[72] = a44;
1424 P[73] = a2 * X[2];

1426 P[75] = a16;
1427 P[76] = a15;
1428 P[77] = a37;
1429 P[78] = a38;

1434 P[83] = a20;
1435 P[84] = a12 * X[2];

1437 P[86] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a22;
1438 P[87] = a23;
1439 P[88] = a2 * a40;
1440 P[89] = (1.0 / 2.0) * a25;
1441 P[90] = a40 * a6;
1442 P[91] = a26;
1443 P[92] = a39;
1444 P[93] = a41;
1445 P[94] = a10 * a40;
1446 P[95] = a45;
1447 P[96] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a28;
1448 P[97] = a0 * a45;
1449 P[98] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a42;
1450 P[99] = a45 * a6;
1451 P[100] = a45 * a7;
1452 P[101] = (1.0 / 4.0) * a30;
1453 P[102] = (1.0 / 4.0) * a31;
1454 P[103] = (1.0 / 4.0) * a43;
1455 P[104] = (1.0 / 5.0) * std::pow(X[2], 5);
1456 return Pm;
1457 }

1464template <>
1465class OrthonormalPolynomialBasis<1, 1>
1466{
1467 public:
1468 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 1;
1469 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 1;
1470 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 2;
1471
1472 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1473 {
1474 Vector<kSize> P;
1475 P[0] = 1;
1476 P[1] = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar> * (2 * X[0] - 1);
1477 return P;
1478 }
1479
1480 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1481 {
1482 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
1483 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
1484 G[0] = 0;
1485 G[1] = 2 * std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar>;
1486 return Gm;
1487 }
1488
1489 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
1490 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1491 {
1492 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
1493 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
1494 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar>;
1495 P[0] = X[0];
1496 P[1] = a0 * ((X[0]) * (X[0])) - a0 * X[0];
1497 return Pm;
1498 }
1499};

1503{

1510 {

1512 P[0] = 1;
1513 P[1] = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar> * (2 * X[0] - 1);
1514 P[2] = std::sqrt(5) * (6 * ((X[0]) * (X[0])) - 6 * X[0] + 1);
1515 return P;
1516 }
1517

1519 {

1524 G[2] = std::sqrt(5) * (12 * X[0] - 6);
1525 return Gm;
1526 }

1528 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
1529 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const

1535 Scalar const a2 = std::sqrt(5);
1536 P[0] = X[0];
1537 P[1] = a0 * a1 - a0 * X[0];
1538 P[2] = -3 * a1 * a2 + 2 * a2 * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0])) + a2 * X[0];
1539 return Pm;

1573 return Gm;
1574 }

1588 P[2] = -3 * a1 * a2 + 2 * a2 * a3 + a2 * X[0];
1589 P[3] =
1590 6 * a1 * a4 - 10 * a3 * a4 + 5 * a4 * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0])) - a4 * X[0];

1625 G[2] = std::sqrt(5) * (12 * X[0] - 6);

1642 P[0] = X[0];

1655template <>
1656class OrthonormalPolynomialBasis<2, 1>
1657{
1658 public:
1659 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 2;
1660 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 1;
1661 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 3;
1662
1663 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1664 {
1665 Vector<kSize> P;
1666 P[0] = std::numbers::sqrt2_v<Scalar>;
1667 P[1] = 2 * (3 * X[0] - 1);
1668 P[2] = 2 * std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar> * (X[0] + 2 * X[1] - 1);
1669 return P;
1670 }
1671
1672 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1673 {
1674 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
1675 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
1676 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar>;
1677 G[0] = 0;
1678 G[1] = 0;
1679 G[2] = 6;
1680 G[3] = 0;
1681 G[4] = 2 * a0;
1682 G[5] = 4 * a0;
1683 return Gm;
1684 }
1685
1686 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
1687 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1688 {
1689 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
1690 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
1691 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt2_v<Scalar>;
1692 Scalar const a1 = 2 * X[0];
1693 Scalar const a2 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
1694 Scalar const a3 = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar>;
1695 Scalar const a4 = 2 * a3;
1696 Scalar const a5 = -a4;
1697 P[0] = a0 * X[0];
1698 P[1] = -a1 + 3 * a2;
1699 P[2] = a2 * a3 + (4 * a3 * X[1] + a5) * X[0];
1700 P[3] = a0 * X[1];
1701 P[4] = 2 * (3 * X[0] - 1) * X[1];
1702 P[5] = a4 * ((X[1]) * (X[1])) + (a1 * a3 + a5) * X[1];
1703 return Pm;
1704 }
1705};

1707template <>
1708class OrthonormalPolynomialBasis<2, 2>
1709{
1710 public:
1711 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 2;
1712 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 2;
1713 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 6;
1714
1715 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1716 {
1717 Vector<kSize> P;
1718 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt2_v<Scalar>;
1719 Scalar const a1 = X[0] + 2 * X[1] - 1;
1720 Scalar const a2 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
1721 Scalar const a3 = 6 * X[1];
1722 P[0] = a0;
1723 P[1] = 2 * (3 * X[0] - 1);
1724 P[2] = 2 * std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar> * a1;
1725 P[3] = std::sqrt(6) * (10 * a2 - 8 * X[0] + 1);
1726 P[4] = 3 * a0 * a1 * (5 * X[0] - 1);
1727 P[5] = std::sqrt(30) * (a2 + a3 * X[0] - a3 - 2 * X[0] + 6 * ((X[1]) * (X[1])) + 1);
1728 return P;
1729 }
1730
1731 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1732 {
1733 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
1734 Scalar* G = Gm.data();
1735 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar>;
1736 Scalar const a1 = std::numbers::sqrt2_v<Scalar>;
1737 Scalar const a2 = a1 * (5 * X[0] - 1);
1738 Scalar const a3 = std::sqrt(30);
1739 G[0] = 0;
1740 G[1] = 0;
1741 G[2] = 6;
1742 G[3] = 0;
1743 G[4] = 2 * a0;
1744 G[5] = 4 * a0;
1745 G[6] = std::sqrt(6) * (20 * X[0] - 8);
1746 G[7] = 0;
1747 G[8] = 15 * a1 * (X[0] + 2 * X[1] - 1) + 3 * a2;
1748 G[9] = 6 * a2;
1749 G[10] = a3 * (2 * X[0] + 6 * X[1] - 2);
1750 G[11] = a3 * (6 * X[0] + 12 * X[1] - 6);
1751 return Gm;
1752 }
1753
1754 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kSize, kDims>
1755 antiderivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1756 {
1757 Matrix<kSize, kDims> Pm;
1758 Scalar* P = Pm.data();
1759 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt2_v<Scalar>;
1760 Scalar const a1 = a0 * X[0];
1761 Scalar const a2 = 2 * X[0];
1762 Scalar const a3 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
1763 Scalar const a4 = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar>;
1764 Scalar const a5 = 2 * a4;
1765 Scalar const a6 = -a5;
1766 Scalar const a7 = std::sqrt(6);
1767 Scalar const a8 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0]));
1768 Scalar const a9 = 3 * a0;
1769 Scalar const a10 = -a9;
1770 Scalar const a11 = a0 * X[1];
1771 Scalar const a12 = std::sqrt(30);
1772 Scalar const a13 = 3 * a12;
1773 Scalar const a14 = 6 * a12;
1774 Scalar const a15 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
1775 Scalar const a16 = 3 * X[0];
1776 P[0] = a1;
1777 P[1] = -a2 + 3 * a3;
1778 P[2] = a3 * a4 + (4 * a4 * X[1] + a6) * X[0];
1779 P[3] = -4 * a3 * a7 + (10.0 / 3.0) * a7 * a8 + a7 * X[0];
1780 P[4] = 5 * a0 * a8 + a3 * (-9 * a0 + 15 * a11) + (-a10 - 6 * a11) * X[0];
1781 P[5] = (1.0 / 3.0) * a12 * a8 + a3 * (-a12 + a13 * X[1]) +
1782 (a12 + a14 * a15 - a14 * X[1]) * X[0];
1783 P[6] = a11;
1784 P[7] = 2 * (a16 - 1) * X[1];
1785 P[8] = a15 * a5 + (a2 * a4 + a6) * X[1];
1786 P[9] = a7 * (10 * a3 - 8 * X[0] + 1) * X[1];
1787 P[10] = a15 * (15 * a1 + a10) + (15 * a0 * a3 - 18 * a1 + a9) * X[1];
1788 P[11] = 2 * a12 * ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1])) + a15 * (a12 * a16 - a13) +
1789 (-a12 * a2 + a12 * a3 + a12) * X[1];
1790 return Pm;
1791 }
1792};

1794template <>
1795class OrthonormalPolynomialBasis<2, 3>
1796{
1797 public:
1798 inline static constexpr std::size_t kDims = 2;
1799 inline static constexpr std::size_t kOrder = 3;
1800 inline static constexpr std::size_t kSize = 10;
1801
1802 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1803 {
1804 Vector<kSize> P;
1805 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt2_v<Scalar>;
1806 Scalar const a1 = X[0] + 2 * X[1] - 1;
1807 Scalar const a2 = 2 * a1;
1808 Scalar const a3 = std::sqrt(6);
1809 Scalar const a4 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));
1810 Scalar const a5 = 6 * X[1];
1811 Scalar const a6 = ((X[1]) * (X[1]));
1812 Scalar const a7 = a4 - 2 * X[0] + 1;
1813 Scalar const a8 = a5 * X[0] - a5 + 6 * a6 + a7;
1814 Scalar const a9 = 10 * X[1];
1815 P[0] = a0;
1816 P[1] = 2 * (3 * X[0] - 1);
1817 P[2] = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar> * a2;
1818 P[3] = a3 * (10 * a4 - 8 * X[0] + 1);
1819 P[4] = 3 * a0 * a1 * (5 * X[0] - 1);
1820 P[5] = std::sqrt(30) * a8;
1821 P[6] = 2 * a0 * (-45 * a4 + 35 * ((X[0]) * (X[0]) * (X[0])) + 15 * X[0] - 1);
1822 P[7] = a2 * a3 * (21 * a4 - 12 * X[0] + 1);
1823 P[8] = 2 * std::sqrt(10) * a8 * (7 * X[0] - 1);
1824 P[9] = std::sqrt(14) * a2 * (10 * a6 + a7 + a9 * X[0] - a9);
1825 return P;
1826 }
1827
1828 [[maybe_unused]] Matrix<kDims, kSize> derivatives([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1829 {
1830 Matrix<kDims, kSize> Gm;
1831 Scalar* G = Gm.data();

1852 Scalar const a20 = a13 * a19;
1853 Scalar const a21 = a19 * (10 * a16 + a17 + a18 * X[0] - a18);
1854 G[0] = 0;
1855 G[1] = 0;
1856 G[2] = 6;
1857 G[3] = 0;
1858 G[4] = 2 * a0;
1859 G[5] = 4 * a0;

1873 G[19] = a20 * (10 * X[0] + 20 * X[1] - 10) + 4 * a21;

1963 [[maybe_unused]] Vector<kSize> eval([[maybe_unused]] Vector<kDims> const& X) const
1964 {
1965 Vector<kSize> P;
1966 Scalar const a0 = std::numbers::sqrt2_v<Scalar>;
1967 Scalar const a1 = X[0] + 2 * X[1] - 1;
1968 Scalar const a2 = 2 * a1;

1970 Scalar const a4 = ((X[0]) * (X[0]));

1983 Scalar const a17 = 140 * ((X[1]) * (X[1]) * (X[1]));
1984 Scalar const a18 = 60 * X[1];
1985 P[0] = a0;
1986 P[1] = 2 * (3 * X[0] - 1);
1987 P[2] = std::numbers::sqrt3_v<Scalar> * a2;
1988 P[3] = a3 * (10 * a4 - 8 * X[0] + 1);
1989 P[4] = 3 * a0 * a1 * (5 * X[0] - 1);
